beer.beer_name: Fat Man Red Suit Big Sack
beer.beer_description:
The ‘Fat Man’ has been created as an Australian Christmas Ale, that combines the rich toffee malt flavours with the big hop aroma and flavour.
Originally brewed for export to Canada this red IPA showcases some of our Aussie Hops. Galaxy, Topaz and Enigma.
